                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#62r">Fol. 62r</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 62r: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቶ፡ ወልደሥላሴ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወለተዮሐንስ፡ ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ገብረ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወስሙ[sic]፡ እሙ፡ ወለተሥላሴሙ[sic]፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ቂርቆስ፡ አድግራት፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መርሐ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in the same poor hand as the main text, in red. According to the note ʾato Wäldä Śǝllase donated the book to the Qirqos church in ʿAddigart. Also the name of Wäldä Śǝllase's wife, Wälättä Yoḥannǝs, father, Gäbrä Yoḥannǝs, and mother, Wälättä Śǝllase, are mentioned.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#62r">Fol. 62r</locus>: Short exhortation to Christ for protection. <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The exhortation is written in a fine hand, in pen. A certain Gäbrä Krǝstos entreats Christ to protect his life.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Pen trials: fol. 62r.&#xD;
- Minor notes, writing exercises, doodles: on the leather cover of the inner faces of both the boards, fols. 3r, 17r, 19rv, 21va, 33rb, 61va, 62rv, 63rv.</item>
                     </list>
